Container.Overview:
Gluetun - VPN client in a thin Docker container for multiple VPN providers, written in Go, and using OpenVPN or Wireguard, DNS over TLS, with a few proxy servers built-in.

'Gluetun-Full' is an attempt to: include ALL of the published paths, ports, &amp; variables available for Gluetun (set to their defaults) from the upstream project, repo, &amp; wiki;
to keep them ALL up-to-date as much as possible; and to include useful Gluetun-Wiki URLs for each config item; all presented in a useful template for the Unraid community.
